* 0.0.10 (Sep 10, 2009) The policy filter
* Adding the check_policy! method, this will return a filter that will check
if the current_user is satisfying a given policy, subject in this action is
optional

* 0.0.9 (Aug 24, 2009) The Rise Of The Generators
* Added a task to the generation of the setup Walruz that runs only the
policies specs
* Replacing the test and spec generated files with new API from Walruz 0.0.9
* Replacing invocations made to Walruz::Manager to Walruz
